{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6c0e0408a4","title":"广西有些社员要求退社","origin":"根据1956年6月28日新华社《内部参考》。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"12d734ac59","index":0,"year":1956,"month":6,"day":28,"articleId":"6c0e0408a4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1a407eb824","name":"陈蓬生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"830de134cb","type":"title","text":"广西有些社员要求退社","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"ae40b5d857","type":"authors","text":"陈蓬生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"e36af877d0","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社南宁28日讯：最近两个多月来，广西省平南、昭平、陆川、玉林、凌乐等县，已有二百来户社员要求退社。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"0a6f68e415","type":"paragraph","text":"田东县三百乡有四个在今年2月间建立的初级社（瑶族人民组成）已经散伙。闹退社的社员，大都是十来户到几十户集体提出要求，有的集体到地委、县委农村工作部去要求批准退社。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"d4a2b1802e","type":"paragraph","text":"退社的原因主要如下：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"35e3dbedb8","type":"paragraph","text":"1·农业社的生产搞得不好，社员情绪不安。劳动管理不好，社员怕吃苦。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"32093fda34","type":"appellation","text":"2·社里对生活困难的社员照顾不够，对社员家庭副业生活没有很好安排。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"28a66e2e03","type":"paragraph","text":"3·社员对粮食统销不满。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"137a176f4b","type":"appellation","text":"4·社干领导作风不民主。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"b3aca53195","type":"paragraph","text":"5·社建工作粗糙，思想发动不充分，生产资料评价入社不合理，建社后对觉悟较低的社员没有及时进行教育，对建社时遗留的问题没有及时解决。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"85e6495487","type":"paragraph","text":"目前，还有些社员表现动摇，存在着“退不退，看分配”的思想。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"1a13ab0d2f","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据1956年6月28日新华社《内部参考》。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"}],"page":{"id":"eadbf409c0","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6c0e0408a4","start":0,"end":0}},"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0f2326230a","type":"paragraph","text":"1·农业社的生产搞得不好，社员情绪不安。劳动管理不好，社员怕吃苦。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"48365de5b1","type":"paragraph","text":"3·社员对粮食统销不满。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"6b4e5b6b84","type":"title","text":"广西有些社员要求退社","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"6e100a6b50","type":"paragraph","text":"5·社建工作粗糙，思想发动不充分，生产资料评价入社不合理，建社后对觉悟较低的社员没有及时进行教育，对建社时遗留的问题没有及时解决。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"7710d521bb","type":"paragraph","text":"田东县三百乡有四个在今年2月间建立的初级社（瑶族人民组成）已经散伙。闹退社的社员，大都是十来户到几十户集体提出要求，有的集体到地委、县委农村工作部去要求批准退社。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"7cfc0f586b","type":"authors","text":"陈蓬生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"8da08fd04e","type":"paragraph","text":"退社的原因主要如下：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"a45953cb78","type":"paragraph","text":"2·社里对生活困难的社员照顾不够，对社员家庭副业生活没有很好安排。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"bf7f25e4a5","type":"paragraph","text":"4·社干领导作风不民主。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6c0e0408a4"},{"id":"d66d6ab242","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社南宁28日讯：最近两个多月来，广西省平南、昭平、陆川、玉林、凌乐等县，已有二百来户社员要求退社。","index":2,"publication